flowchart LR
    INTENT[Intent: IN_PROGRESS]

    INTENT --> NEED{approval needed?}
    NEED -->|no| EXEC[execute]
    NEED -->|yes| WAIT[WAITING_FOR_HUMAN]
    WAIT --> INBOX[Approver Inbox]
    INBOX --> DECISION{decision}
    DECISION -->|approve| RESUME[resume intent]
    DECISION -->|reject| CANCEL[CANCELED]
    DECISION -->|timeout| TIMEOUT[WAITING_FOR_TIME → timeout]
    RESUME --> EXEC
    EXEC --> DONE[COMPLETED]
    TIMEOUT --> CANCEL
